	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=202818"><span id="Scholar">Bilboh</span></a><br /><b><span id="Scholar">Scholar</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">22 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Decent [3.17]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Just wanted to add a couple things.&nbsp;&nbsp;If Rhozth Ssrakezh is up you better be VERY careful unless you have fade.  He is now NOT on a 7 day timer.  I'd say its closer to 4-8 hours now.  Do not set up camp in Yelwinz's room unless you can FM or a group that can take Rhozth  down (and any bard that needs VoTS probably would die very quickly to him - He's a level 60 SK that hits in the 400's, has at least 50k hps, LARGE melee range, and has a nasty curse).  He does NOT assist Yelwinz or his PH, so you can pull them when he is up, but make sure you have a mez or stun up when fighting because if they gate and summon you, you will be in trouble as he WILL aggro.  He has the XTC healing curse which makes all heals on you 75% less effective, so make sure if you get hit by it you get an RGC or RC (3 shots) right away.<br/><br/>Note:  I got my VoTS after 8 Yelwinz kills and probably 24 PH.  Expect a 8-10 hour camp.  Any less and you are very lucky.</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
